==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Airing
<hw>Air"ing</hw> <pr>(⟦acir⟧r"⟦icr⟧ng)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>A walk or a ride in the open air; a short excursion for health's
sake.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An exposure to air, or to a fire, for warming,
drying, etc.; <as>as, the <ex>airing</ex> of linen, or of a
room</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Air jacket</ent>⟦br⟧
